00:17:32.432 --> 00:17:36.152
So we asked whether this was true. We did an in vitro assay first

302
00:17:36.752 --> 00:17:39.512
where we plated cells with fluorescent collagen.

303
00:17:40.192 --> 00:17:43.852
We then placed our tumor cells on top, either the

304
00:17:43.972 --> 00:17:47.752
wild type cells or the legumen knockout cells, and then monitored them for

