00:17:51.712 --> 00:17:55.172
In one arm of the experiment, we added a cathepsin inhibitor,

307
00:17:55.552 --> 00:17:58.412
E64d, on two days, on day three and day five.

308
00:17:58.592 --> 00:18:02.432
So this is what it looks like. So on day three, you can see that the

